helptext pressure_help = "FIREMAIN CTA PRESSURE SENSORS------------


This object displays the new Fire Main CTA pressure sensor located 
adjacent to the passenger subway between carpark 1A and Terminal 1.


The pressure can be monitored in psi or bar. To change the displayed 
pressure use the right hand mouse button over the corresponding units button.


There are no controls associated with this object, it is purely for monitoring
only. However it is possible to set high and low level alarms, and to set / clear tagged 
messages via the menu controls using the mouse.
"
